"a.切线的；离题的 【英】 adj.切线的 (of the nature of a tangent)；离题的 (divergent, digressive) 【考】 反义词：gist(要点)- tangential point(非要点) 【例】 tangential remarks(离题的话) adj. 切线的; 离题的 【反】gist(n 要点)－tangential point(非要点) 【记】切线不在中心，离题 tangential (adj.)  1620s, see tangent (adj.) + -ial. Figurative sense of ""divergent, erratic"" is from 1787; that of ""slightly connected"" is from 1825. Related: Tangentially."
